title: Watch: HIGH4 Releases Cute And Playful Music Video For “Love Line”
text:
Check out HIGH4’s new music video for their title song “Love Line” from the album “Blessed”! 
The video is a compilation of HIGH4 doing everything from goofing off to professionally posing for photo shoots, and it will have fans reminiscing about all of HIGH4’s activities from their debut until now. 
Meanwhile, it was previously revealed that Sunggu would be leaving the group after HIGH4’s Japanese activities in March. 
Watch the video below!
